/ ************* Tutorial 3 ************** /

/ Task 1: MARIE basic

/ ************** Hard code ************** /
Load 004
/ Load value from address 004 into AC
Add 004
/ Add value from address 004 to value in AC
Store 004
/ Store AC into address 004
Halt
/ Stop execution
DEC 42
/ This is address 004, initialise with value 42

/ ************** Rewritting the program ************** /
Input
/ Input a value x
Store x
/ Store AC into address x
Input
/ Input another value y
Store y
/ Store AC into address y
Load x
/ Load value from address x into AC
Add y
/ Add value from address y to value in AC
Store Z
/ Store AC into address Z
Output
/ Prints value from AC
Halt
/ Stop execution
x, Dec 0
y, Dec 0
Z, Dec 0

/ Task 2 /

/ C := 0
/ AC = 0
Clear
/ AC -> C == STORE 0 AT C
Store C
/ if A=0 then jump to line 06 000 (AC < 0) 400 (AC = 0) 800 (AC > 0)
Input
/ Input a value A /
Store A
/ store that value in address A /
Input
/ Input a value B /
Store B
/ Store that value in address B /
loop, Load A
	Skipcond 800
      Jump end
      / C := C+b
      Load C
      Add B
      Store C
      / A := A-1
      Load A
      Subt One
      Store A
      / Jump to line 2
      Jump loop
end, Halt

/ ***************** Variables ******************* /
A, DEC x
B, DEC y
C, DEC z 
/ x, y, z can be any numbers /

/ ***************** Constants ******************* /
One, DEC 1
